OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,F'We're not there yet': JD Vance says
OL,7,Fmore work to be done on deal with Iran
OL,9,FThe US and Iran still have several
OL,10,Fimportant details to iron out before
OL,11,Fthey can reach an agreement to end the
OL,12,Fwar, Vice President JD Vance has said.
OL,14,FIt comes after Washington and Tehran
OL,15,Freached a tentative agreement on
OL,16,FThursday to extend a ceasefire between
OL,17,Fthe two nations by 60 days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
