PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FThey also plan to launch talks on
OL,7,FTehran's nuclear programme, according
OL,8,Fto a US official with knowledge of the
OL,9,Ftalks.
OL,11,FSpeaking to reporters before catching
OL,12,Fa helicopter at Joint Base Andrews,
OL,13,FMaryland, the US vice president said
OL,14,Fthere was still plenty of work to be
OL,15,Fdone to secure a longer-term peace
OL,16,Fdeal ` particularly on the question of
OL,17,FIran's nuclear capabilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,F"There are certain details that are
OL,7,Fgoing to have to be figured out, that
OL,8,Fare going to take a little bit of time
OL,9,Fto figure out," he said.
OL,11,F"Just take, for example, even if you
OL,12,Fcome to an agreement on, let's say,
OL,13,Fdestroying the enriched stockpile, how
OL,14,Fdo you do it? When do you do it? How
OL,15,Fdo you actually get access to it?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FVance added: "I think there's always a
OL,7,Fconcern whenever you're in a
OL,8,Fnegotiation that the other party is
OL,9,Fnot actually going to meet up their
OL,10,Fobligation, they're actually not going
OL,11,Fto satisfy their end of the
OL,12,Fobligation, but all you can do is try
OL,13,Fto verify, right?
OL,15,F"You don't take anything on faith,
OL,16,Feven the guarantee that they do not
OL,17,Fbuild or procure a nuclear programme,
OL,18,Fwhich is something they have agreed
OL,19,Fto, we're going to have to verify that
OL,20,Fover time."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FVance reiterated that the US military
OL,7,Fhad "decimated" Iran's military and
OL,8,Fclaimed they were in a position "where
OL,9,Fwe could substantially set back their
OL,10,Fnuclear programme, not just during the
OL,11,Fterm of this president but over the
OL,12,Flong term".
OL,14,F"That's a very, very good thing for
OL,15,Fthe American peopl," he added. "So,
OL,16,Fwe're not there yet, but we're very
OL,17,Fclose and we're going to keep on
OL,18,Fworking at it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
