OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FIt is understood that President Donald
OL,7,FTrump has yet to give his final
OL,8,Fapproval of a 60-day memorandum of
OL,9,Funderstanding (MoU) between the US and
OL,10,FIran.
OL,12,FThe 60-day MoU will state that
OL,13,Fshipping transiting the Strait of
OL,14,FHormuz will be "unrestricted",
OL,15,Faccording to a report by US outlet
OL,16,FAxios, citing US officials and sources.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FA US official was quoted as saying
OL,7,Fthat this means no tolls and no
OL,8,Fharassment and that Iran will have to
OL,9,Fremove all mines from the strait
OL,10,Fwithin 30 days.
OL,12,FA source close to Iran's negotiating
OL,13,Fteam has denied relevant reports by
OL,14,FWestern media claiming that the text
OL,15,Fof a proposed MoU between Iran and the
OL,16,FUS had been finalised, Iran's semi-
OL,17,Fofficial Tasnim news agency reported
OL,18,Fon Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FThe source told Tasnim that reports
OL,7,Fsuggesting the text was merely
OL,8,Fawaiting formal announcement by the
OL,9,Ftwo sides were "not consistent with
OL,10,Fthe facts", adding that the document
OL,11,F"has not yet been finalised".
OL,13,FAccording to the source, Iran has not
OL,14,Fformally informed Pakistani mediators
OL,15,Fthat the text has been completed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
