OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FThe latest developments came as the
OL,7,Ffragile seven-week ceasefire between
OL,8,Fthe US and Iran appeared to be
OL,9,Fwavering, with both sides repeatedly
OL,10,Faccusing each other of violating it in
OL,11,Fthe last few days.
OL,13,FEarlier on Thursday, US Central
OL,14,FCommand said Kuwait had intercepted
OL,15,Fmissiles from Iran on Wednesday night,
OL,16,Fwith military officials calling the
OL,17,Fincident an "egregious ceasefire
OL,18,Fviolation".
OL,26,@yD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
