OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FIran said it had fired on a US base in
OL,7,Fa Gulf state it did not name in
OL,8,Fretaliation for strikes earlier in the
OL,9,Fweek, making it unclear if the
OL,10,Fmissiles were intended to hit Kuwait.
OL,12,FThe Kuwaiti Foreign Ministry condemned
OL,13,FIran for what it called "blatant
OL,14,Faggression".
OL,16,FAmerican forces had shot down four one-
OL,17,Fway attack drones around the Strait of
OL,18,FHormuz and hit a ground-control
OL,19,Fstation in Bandar Abbas that was about
OL,20,Fto launch a fifth, US officials said
OL,21,Fon Wednesday evening.
OL,26,@uD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FOn Monday, the US also conducted what
OL,7,Fthe Pentagon called "self-defence"
OL,8,Fstrikes on missile launch sites and
OL,9,Fminelaying boats in southern Iran.
OL,11,FDespite the attacks, Trump has
OL,12,Finsisted his administration is making
OL,13,Fheadway in the talks.
OL,15,FThe US president wants the Strait of
OL,16,FHormuz to be fully reopened and for
OL,17,FIran to give up its stockpile of
OL,18,Fhighly enriched uranium.
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
