OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780081925
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'very close' to striking
OL,4,Cdeal but 'not there yet', JD Vance says
OL,6,FThe Islamic Republic is looking for
OL,7,Feconomic sanctions to be lifted and
OL,8,Ffrozen assets to be released to aid
OL,9,Fits shattered economy.
OL,11,FAny deal between the countries must
OL,12,Falso include an end to Israel's
OL,13,Fmilitary operations in Lebanon against
OL,14,Fthe Iranian-backed militant group
OL,15,FHezbollah, Iran has insisted.
